---
title: Sumac Meatballs and Crisp Cucumber Salad with Sultana Couscous
description: Sumac spiced meatballs are paired with a (soon to be favourite) crisp, crunchy and vinegary cucumber and red onion salad. Sultana raisin flecked couscous takes this dish to the lighter side!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-au-sumac-et-salade-croquante-de-concombres-fe5a62fd.jpg
